<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Conjuration" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Conjuration,</orth> 1) incantation: <cit><quote>buz these --s in her brain,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.2.99" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 2, 99</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>what c. and what mighty magic,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 1.3.92" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 3, 92</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) obsecration: <cit><quote>mock not my senseless c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 3.2.23" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 III, 2, 23</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>under this c. speak,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 1.2.29" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 I, 2, 29</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I do defy thy --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 5.3.68" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom V, 3, 68</bibl></cit> (Q<hi rend="sub">2</hi> <emph>commiration,</emph> Ff <emph>commiseration</emph>). <cit><quote>an earnest c. from the king,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 5.2.38" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 2, 38</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>